body:
Hi @iphydf

Long time no see. It seems like you want to restart development on qTox.

If you (and a team?) are able to continue the work I'd be happy to redirect qTox/qTox to here.

Let me know what you think about it.

comment_data.body:
Hi :) yeah, we've started working on it again. I'd like to revive it properly. We're aiming for a 1.18 release pretty soon. The team is mainly me, @Green-Sky, and @robinlinden at the moment. Maybe more people will want to join.

For the release, we should probably point the download page on qtox.github.io at the new URLs.
@sudden6 I think we're ready for this change now.
